# NPM Token Configuration Template
# Copy this file to ~/.npmrc and add your token

# Option 1: Simple token
#//registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=npm_your_token_here

# Option 2: Granular token with metadata
#//registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=npm_your_token_here
#//registry.npmjs.org/:token-spec=mclaude@1.6.0

# Security tips:
# - Never commit .npmrc with real tokens to git
# - Use environment variables in CI/CD: ${NPM_TOKEN}
# - Token expires in 7 days (per your specification)
# - MFA required for publishing
